{"tid":1628535,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「文宣」琴日有裝修師傅去錯匯豐裝修","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:25:56.000Z","uid":40999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc893f7f2999075c7c576addb832849da94cfbe","tid":1628535,"uid":40999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"見到有位好有心嘅巴打向上商登報道歉及賠償，呢類文宣非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌登報向上海商業銀行道歉 道歉信草案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n其實琴日匯豐都被裝修，文宣一拼處理大家點睇？<br />\n另外，琴晚360樓上受火魔法影響嘅市民，應否製作文宣道歉？<br />\n<br />\n前線攞條命出嚟，後排可以做嘅，係令件事更加完美，令前線更安心。民意唔會立即令民主降臨，但政府最怕嘅就係民意一直都不逆轉，而民意高昂除咗警隊不斷犯錯之外，最大原因係大家互不割蓆，互保不足。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"2a1cb1905b1fd04ad5f6c6c641f9669b36415bcf","tid":1628535,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"匯豐都俾人搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f87e4ee09af32b9a4b4b49127f6e5d22eab352","tid":1628535,"uid":40999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a1cb1905b1fd04ad5f6c6c641f9669b36415bcf","tid":1628535,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"匯豐都俾人搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"係呀，琴日有相，唔知有冇巴打搵得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線好有心，係下面寫咗句sorry:(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1541c6c82e2d03ed212559fb698bb8f163ab7ee","tid":1628535,"uid":263186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"訓係到都中槍"},{"pid":"afadc21495a977257504e8a840b93098b861b6ea","tid":1628535,"uid":33952,"like":1,"dislike":0